    <ul>
      <li>Given <code>0,3,6</code>, the <code>30000000</code>th number spoken is <code>175594</code>.</li>
      <li>Given <code>1,3,2</code>, the <code>30000000</code>th number spoken is <code>2578</code>.</li>
